A generic implementation of a Load Balancer and Fail over mechanism

Feature
=======
1 Multi protocol support
2 Any Text based(HTTP) or Binary protocol(SMPP) server can be supported
3 Supports 3 modes of operation
4 Fail Over (If one goes down transfer load to the other)
5 Load Balancer (distribute equal load among the pool of servers)
6 Online Routing (using the admin port fire online routing commands)
7 Good performance (Code is written in C++)
8 SSL support present
9 Persistent or Non-persistent connections to the pool supported